---
const title = "AmicBridge | Private Borrow & Lend Network";
const description =
  "AmicBridge is a private person-to-person network where verified members can request to borrow, lend, or work together on investments. AmicBridge never holds client funds.";
---

<head>
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f5f7;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --border: #d3d6de;
      --text: #111827;
      --muted: #4b5563;
      --accent: #1f4fd8;
      --danger: #b91c1c;
      --font: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
        sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--font);
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 880px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 16px 40px;
    }

    header {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: right;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .intro {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 14px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .col {
      flex: 1 1 260px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 14px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    ul {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .form-section {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 14px 18px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    form {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px 16px;
    }

    .field {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .field.full {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    label {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    label span {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    input,
    select,
    textarea {
      font-family: var(--font);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 7px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 70px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    input:focus,
    select:focus,
    textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hint {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .checkbox-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .checkbox-row input[type="checkbox"] {
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      justify-self: flex-start;
    }

    button:hover {
      filter: brightness(1.05);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 10px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .warning {
      color: var(--danger);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .tagline {
        text-align: left;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<main>
  <header>
    <div class="brand">AmicBridge</div>
    <div class="tagline">
      Private borrow, lend &amp; invest<br />Person-to-person network
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Request to borrow, lend, or invest through AmicBridge</h1>
    <p class="note">
      AmicBridge is a private network bridge. Members can request to
      <strong>borrow money</strong>, <strong>lend money</strong>, or work
      together on <strong>investments</strong>. We carefully check members with
      ID verification before matching them with others in the network.
    </p>
    <p class="note">
      AmicBridge does <strong>not</strong> hold or move funds. All money is
      transferred directly between members under their own agreements.
      AmicBridge charges a <strong>5% fee</strong> on every deal made through
      the network.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h2>Borrowers</h2>
      <p class="note">
        Send a request if you want to borrow money using a private loan
        agreement.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Choose currency: NOK, USD, EUR, or crypto.</li>
        <li>Explain how much you need and for how long.</li>
        <li>Describe your work, income and ability to repay.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <h2>Lenders</h2>
      <p class="note">
        Send a request if you want to lend money to verified members.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Set what kind of borrowers you prefer.</li>
        <li>Choose currencies and loan sizes you are open to.</li>
        <li>Decide yourself which deals you accept.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <h2>Investments</h2>
      <p class="note">
        You can also ask for investment strategy help or co-investment
        opportunities.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Describe your financial goals and risk level.</li>
        <li>Ask for ideas to grow your money.</li>
        <li>We only connect verified members; we never hold funds.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="form-section">
    <h2>Request to join the private network</h2>
    <p class="note">
      Fill in the form below to send a request to AmicBridge. We review your
      details and then contact you for ID verification and follow-up. After
      that we can try to match you with other verified members.
    </p>

    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xzznjkvd" method="POST">
      <!-- Basic information -->
      <div class="field">
        <label for="fullName">Full name <span>*</span></label>
        <input
          id="fullName"
          name="full_name"
          type="text"
          autocomplete="name"
          required
        />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="age">Age <span>*</span></label>
        <input id="age" name="age" type="number" min="18" required />
        <div class="hint">You must be at least 18 years old.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="email">Email <span>*</span></label>
        <input
          id="email"
          name="email"
          type="email"
          autocomplete="email"
          required
        />
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="country">Country of residence <span>*</span></label>
        <input id="country" name="country" type="text" required />
      </div>

      <!-- Purpose -->
      <div class="field">
        <label for="role">What do you want to do? <span>*</span></label>
        <select id="role" name="role" required>
          <option value="">Select one</option>
          <option value="borrow">Request to borrow money</option>
          <option value="lend">Offer to lend money</option>
          <option value="both">Borrow and lend</option>
          <option value="invest">Investment / strategy only</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="currency">Preferred currency <span>*</span></label>
        <select id="currency" name="currency" required>
          <option value="">Select currency</option>
          <option value="NOK">NOK</option>
          <option value="USD">USD</option>
          <option value="EUR">EUR</option>
          <option value="CRYPTO">Crypto (specify below)</option>
        </select>
        <div class="hint">
          If you choose crypto, add which asset in the message field.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Work & income -->
      <div class="field">
        <label for="employment">Work situation <span>*</span></label>
        <select id="employment" name="employment_status" required>
          <option value="">Select one</option>
          <option value="full_time">Employed – full time</option>
          <option value="part_time">Employed – part time</option>
          <option value="self_employed">Self-employed</option>
          <option value="student">Student</option>
          <option value="unemployed">Unemployed</option>
          <option value="retired">Retired</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="income">
          Monthly net income (approx.) <span>*</span>
        </label>
        <input
          id="income"
          name="monthly_income"
          type="text"
          placeholder="Example: 30 000 NOK"
          required
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Borrow details -->
      <div class="field full">
        <label for="loanDetails">If you want to borrow: loan details</label>
        <textarea
          id="loanDetails"
          name="loan_details"
          placeholder="Amount, purpose of the loan, how long, repayment plan, any collateral, etc."
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <!-- Lender preferences -->
      <div class="field full">
        <label for="lenderPreferences">
          If you want to lend: preferred borrowers
        </label>
        <textarea
          id="lenderPreferences"
          name="lender_preferences"
          placeholder="Income level, country, risk level, minimum/maximum amounts, purpose of loan you accept, etc."
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <!-- Investment strategy -->
      <div class="field full">
        <label for="investment">
          Investment &amp; strategy requests
        </label>
        <textarea
          id="investment"
          name="investment_request"
          placeholder="Describe if you want help with an investment strategy or to find co-investors."
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <!-- Extra information -->
      <div class="field full">
        <label for="extra">Anything else we should know?</label>
        <textarea
          id="extra"
          name="extra_information"
          placeholder="For example: experience with loans/investments, risk tolerance, how you heard about AmicBridge."
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <!-- Confirmations -->
      <div class="field full">
        <div class="checkbox-row">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            id="confirmNotBank"
            name="confirm_not_bank"
            required
          />
          <label for="confirmNotBank">
            I understand that AmicBridge is a private matching network, not a
            bank or broker, and that AmicBridge does not hold or control funds.
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field full">
        <div class="checkbox-row">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            id="confirmRisk"
            name="confirm_risk"
            required
          />
          <label for="confirmRisk">
            I understand that borrowing, lending and investing involve risk and
            that I am responsible for my own decisions. Nothing from
            AmicBridge is personal financial advice.
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field full">
        <div class="checkbox-row">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            id="confirmFee"
            name="confirm_fee"
            required
          />
          <label for="confirmFee">
            I understand that AmicBridge takes a 5% fee on every deal that is
            made with someone in the AmicBridge network.
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button type="submit">Send request</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>How matching works</h3>
      <p class="note">
        When we receive your request, we review the information, contact you
        for ID verification, and then decide if we can approve you for the
        private network. If approved, we will only match you with other
        verified members whose profile fits your request.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <h3>Agreements and funds</h3>
      <p class="note">
        Matches are introductions only. You and the other person agree on your
        own contract and move funds directly between yourselves using the
        payment methods you choose. AmicBridge never touches the money.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <h3>Risk and responsibility</h3>
      <p class="note">
        Every deal carries risk, including the possibility of losing money.
        Only enter into agreements you fully understand, follow the laws in
        your country, and consider getting independent professional advice for
        important financial decisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>
      <strong>AmicBridge</strong> is a private network bridge for people who
      want to borrow, lend, or invest directly with each other.
    </p>
    <p class="warning">
      AmicBridge is not a bank, investment firm, broker, or financial adviser.
      We do not guarantee returns, repayments, or the behavior of any member.
    </p>
  </footer>
</main>
